# Executive Summary

## Business Problem
The company is facing customer churn and inconsistent sales performance.

## Objectives
- Reduce churn
- Increase customer retention
- Improve profitability

## Key Findings
- High monthly charges increase churn probability
- Short-tenure customers are more likely to leave
- Some regions generate higher sales and profit

## Recommendations
- Introduce loyalty programs
- Offer long-term discounts
- Improve onboarding experience

## Expected Impact
- 15% reduction in churn
- 10% increase in sales
- Improved customer satisfaction